			<header class="article-header">

                                                                        <div class="series-header">
                        <p class="series-title"><a href="https://www.propublica.org/series/gutting-the-irs" aria-label="In the series: Gutting the IRS">Gutting the IRS</a></p>
                                            </div>
                                    
				<h2 class="hed">How the IRS Was Gutted</h2>
								<p class="dek">An eight-year campaign to slash the agency’s budget has left it understaffed, hamstrung and operating with archaic equipment. The result: billions less to fund the government. That’s good news for corporations and the wealthy.</p>
								<div class="metadata">
					<p class="byline">by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/paul-kiel">Paul Kiel</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jesse-eisinger">Jesse Eisinger</a></p>
					<time class="timestamp" datetime="2018-12-11EST05:00">Dec. 11, 2018, 5 a.m. EST</time>
				</div>

			
