					    <img alt=""  width="400" height="267" src="https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/series/_threeTwo400w/2019829-Gutting-the-IRS-3000x2000.jpg" srcset="https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/series/_threeTwo400w/2019829-Gutting-the-IRS-3000x2000.jpg 400w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/series/_threeTwo800w/2019829-Gutting-the-IRS-3000x2000.jpg 800w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/series/_threeTwo1200w/2019829-Gutting-the-IRS-3000x2000.jpg 1200w" />
				    </a>
			    </div>
		    			    <div class="description">
					<div class="series-header">
						<h3 class="series-title"><a href="https://www.propublica.org/series/gutting-the-irs"><span class="a11y">Series: </span>Gutting the IRS</a></h3>
											<p class="series-description">Who Wins When a Crucial Agency Is Defunded</p>
										</div>
			    </div>
